in immediate distress</li></ul></div><div style=\"background-color: #e8f5e9; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #2e7d32;\">Crisis Resources:</p><ul style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"padding: 5px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #333;\"><strong>National Crisis Hotline:</strong> 988</li><li style=\"padding: 5px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #333;\"><strong>Crisis Text Line:</strong> Text HOME to 741741</li></ul></div><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; font-weight: 500;\">You don't have to face this alone. We're here to help.</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px;\">With care,<br><strong>Your Wellness Team</strong></p></div></div>",
